		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="414" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">微末进行旋转、坠拳2段攻击，均造成<span color="#ffe599">60%</span><span>伤害；坠拳产生向前的多段岩击波，造成</span><span color="#ffe599">70%,35%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="437" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">微末进行左右交拿、纵拳3段攻击，分别造成<span color="#ffe599">50%,50%,80%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="511" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">距离较远时，微末举起岩石，朝玩家丢来，造成<span color="#ffe599">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="511" width="423" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">距离较远时，微末化为巨石翻滚而来，移至目标处立即接一纵拳，造成<span color="#ffe599">90%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="799" width="439" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">微末将双拳强化，朝地板进行3次撼地猛击，依次造成<span color="#ffe599">50%,50%,100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="799" width="442" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">微末自身附属<span textDecoration="underline">垩甲</span><span>，以及一条独立的热量。垩甲未坏时，微末将不受到伤害；热量填满时，微末将过载陷入瘫痪，40s内不会重新出现热量条，否则将持续维持高抗性。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
