		<RichText x="66" y="972" width="436" height="78" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">「过载燃烧」：热量上限944。微末受到<span color="#ff9999">火元素</span><span>攻击后，会根据火元素的量积攒</span><span color="#ffdfbf">2.119n%</span><span>(20n)或</span><span color="#ffdfbf">0.742%</span><span>(7)热量，攒满后进入虚耗状态，该状态下会失去抗性提升。<br/>垩甲：</span><span color="#ffe599">40岩</span><span>盾，击破后允许受到伤害，90s内不会恢复。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
